---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<style>
  body {
    display: grid;
    align-content: space-between;
    row-gap: 24px;

    width: 100vw;
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    overflow-y: auto;

    padding: 50px;
    box-sizing: border-box;

    font-family: system-ui, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif,
      "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol";
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 62px;
    line-height: 1;

    background-color: #ededed;
  }

  footer {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    column-gap: 24px;
    row-gap: 44px;
  }

  .footer-item {
    display: flex;
  }

  #socials-group {
    flex-direction: row;
    column-gap: 24px;
    row-gap: 44px;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 1479px) {
    #email {
      order: 2;
    }
    #cta {
      order: 1;
      width: 100%;
    }
    #socials-group {
      order: 3;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 1034px) {
    .footer-item {
      width: 100%;
    }

    #email {
      order: 3;
    }
    #socials-group {
      order: 2;
    }
  }

  .social {
    display: flex;
    place-content: center;
    place-items: center;

    background-color: #d9d9d9;
    border-radius: 100%;
    width: 91px;
    height: 91px;
    font-size: 32px;
    line-height: 36px;
  }
</style>

<Layout title="">
  <main>
    Мартин Леженин — графический дизайнер, медиахудожник, куратор, арт-директор,
    педагог, креативный директор, бренд-директор, и основатель креативного бюро
    Whale Studio.
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-item" id="email">
      <a>martin@lezhen.in</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-item" id="cta">
      <a>ПОРАБОТАЕМ?</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-item" id="socials-group">
      <a class="social">IG</a>
      <a class="social">LI</a>
      <a class="social">TG</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
